. Install Nodejs

> brew install node

. Express 

Express Web Development Framework for Node.js

. Create Sample NODEJS App
> npm init 
> touch index.js

. add Express 
> npm install express --save

NPM Versioning
==============
^ Ex: ^4.13.3 install any mayor version
~ Ex: ~4.13.x  install any minor version

START EXPRES App
================
. Open Index.js

var express = require('express');
var app = express();
var port = 5000;

app.get('/', function(req, res) {
    res.send('Hello World');
});

app.listen(port, function(err) {
    console.log('running server on port' + port);
});

. Open package.json
"start": "node index.js"

. start application
> npm start

. if an error is thrown when executing npm start, remove node_modules
> rm -fr node_modules








